    <section>
        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>The Pakistan Super League (PSL) is gearing up for its tenth edition with the player draft scheduled for January 13, 2025, at Huzoori Bagh, Lahore Fort. This event, marking a decade of the league, will begin with a ceremony at 12:30 PM and promises live broadcast coverage. Fans can also engage online with the event's official hashtag, <span class="hashtag">#DECADEOFHBLPSL</span>, and participate in the PSL Fans Choice Awards 2025 for a chance to win tickets. This draft follows the IPL auction, enabling teams to strategize their picks potentially influenced by IPL outcomes.</p>
